  "L4Q43": "13. What is Jesus doing now?",
  "L4B44":
      "'I am going to PREPARE A PLACE FOR YOU. And if I go and prepare a place for you, I will come again and receive you to Myself, so that where I am, there you may be also.' - John 14:2, 3.",
  "L4P45":
